headline: 'Dear Salman Rushdie…': Isabelle Adjani's stand against religious fundamentalism
description: 'Adjani, The Famous Stranger' (4/6). After Iran issued a fatwa against the British writer in 1989, the French actress used the César Awards ceremony to show her support for the author of 'The Satanic Verses.' She was one of the few in the film industry to take such a stand.
